article_title: Mayo Clinic: Raises on the way
article_text:
Rochester, MN (55903)

Today

Mostly cloudy skies early, then partly cloudy in the afternoon. A stray shower or thunderstorm is possible. High 83F. Winds WSW at 10 to 15 mph..

Tonight

Mostly clear skies early. Scattered showers and thunderstorms developing later during the night. Low 61F. Winds SSE at 10 to 15 mph. Chance of rain 50%.

article_metadata.author: Jeff Hansel, jhansel@postbulletin.com

og.description: Mayo Clinic will offer across-the-board salary increases in 2014, the Post-Bulletin has learned.
